ED_Title: Closing date of the seventy-fourth session of the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: On 12 August 2020, the General Assembly, on the proposal of its President (A/74/L.79), decided to postpone the closing date of the seventy-fourth session of the Assembly to Tuesday, 15 September 2020.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/74/49 (Vol. III)) after editorial review.
